706917f-a.title: Brooklyn: Strong Place - Kane Street
706917f-a.text:
2-8 Strong Place, west side, south from Kane Street. No. 2 is at the
S.W. corner of Kane Street. Also seen is 162-164 Kane Street, south side,
west from Strong Place to Henry Street.
AAvgust 5, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
